## Hints for Future Agents
- claims_genai MUST be computed from the original Span (span_claims_genai), NOT
  the extracted row. Extraction is lossy on presence. If you move validation
  earlier/later, preserve this.
- _ended_before_started compares tz-normalized: SENTINEL_EPOCH is tz-AWARE but
  extraction builds NAIVE datetimes; a raw `<` across the two raises TypeError.
  Mirrors ch_sentinel_values from_ch_value's tz-insensitive compare.
- 5 pre-existing mypy errors in agents/clickhouse.py (lines ~241/243/255/257/438
  on master: str->Literal in pydantic ctor calls via safe_str). They appear in
  single-file mypy mode and are NOT mine; verified by stashing my diff.
- The FastAPI route that maps the response to OTLP partial-success is in
  wandb/core services/weave-trace, not this repo. To actually ENFORCE rejection
  in prod, set WEAVE_GENAI_OTEL_REJECT_SHAPE_ERRORS=true on the weave-trace
  server deployment.
- Did NOT edit AGENTS.md (repo rule asks to, but this user reverted AGENTS.md
  edits in a prior stack; in-module docstrings cover the new concept). Revisit
